column2: SELECT   s.ra, s.dec,s.z,s.zErr,s.velDisp, s.velDispErr, s.survey, s.programname, s.mjd, s.plate, s.fiberid, l.h_alpha_cont, l.h_alpha_flux, l.h_alpha_eqw, l.oii_#_cont, l.oii_#_flux, l.oii_#_eqw, l.oii_#_cont, l.oii_#_flux, l.oii_#_eqw, l.h_beta_cont, l.h_beta_flux, l.h_beta_eqw into mydb.legacy_only_galaxy_lines from specObj as s JOIN photoObj as p   ON p.objID = s.bestObjID JOIN galSpecLine as l   ON s.specObjID = l.specObjID JOIN galSpecIndx as i   ON s.specObjID = i.specObjID  WHERE   s.programname = &&& AND s.class = &&&
